><dc:creator><![CDATA[AjKaramba]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Successful extraction from a bad situation. UPDATE.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/bI6NSnX</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jdpaI5G.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So the other day I posted a question about the anonymity of Uber/Lyft rides because they were going to order one to my place. Imgur suggested that I reach out to local shelters for help. 

Because my friend’s phone is closely monitored by the ex I did it all myself so that there was less chance of them getting caught.

A nice person at the first shelter I called agreed to order the ride with their company account and used their location as a neutral meeting place. They took down my information (just in case I was someone trying to take advantage of them) and verified that my friend was going with me willingly. 

A cop was on scene as well and took my friend’s official statement that they don’t want their location divulged to their ex. Now they are in my spare bedroom and snoozing peacefully.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/bI6NSnX</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LordOfZajo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>“You won’t ever steal from me again”</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AZJd5en</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/H7Gr7pT.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://youtu.be/dPN9vJf92Fs</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/AZJd5en</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SpottieOttieDopaliciousAngel]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Stoked!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RQWtbU1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qpZoLOp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yassss!  I’m really happy guys. :)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RQWtbU1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JoeyKillface]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>balloon-ympics</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/rgolPZG</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5vTEY6d.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gGdk3Ys.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/rgolPZG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[zoraniko]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Attention!!! Dump of random possibly interesting stuff</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/nRkbrHn</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zI0VjIW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/55y09XE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur